window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Winner takes all.</b></p> <p>Honorable deeds and Legendary cities are the name of the game.</p> <p>The money-hungry bosses in charge of New Realm Online have installed a new quest and screwed over the medi pod users. But the quest rewards would give Ryan and the rest of the Broken Bones guild the ability to afford to stay in this magical world.</p> <p>The competition will be fierce! Ryan and the team will have to be bold, level up, and take some risks if they want to win!</p> <p>This book contains classic LitRPG elements of leveling, dungeons, terrifying killer bunnies, crafting, and community building. No harem.</p>"; 
